atcher]]\n|[[Arizona Wildcats baseball|Arizona]]\n|-\n|24\n|[[Max Meyer (baseball)|Max Meyer]]\n|[[Pitcher]]\n|[[Minnesota Golden Gophers baseball|Minnesota]]\n|-\n|25\n|Pete Crow-Armstrong\n|[[Outfielder]]\n|[[Harvard-Westlake School]] ([[California|CA]])\n|-\n|26\n|Drew Romo\n|[[Catcher]]\n|[[The Woodlands High School]] ([[Texas|TX]])\n|-\n|27\n|[[Cole Wilcox]]\n|[[Pitcher]]\n|[[Georgia Bulldogs baseball|Georgia]]\n|-\n|28\n|[[Cade Cavalli]]\n|[[Pitcher]]\n|[[Oklahoma Sooners baseball|Oklahoma]]\n|-\n|29\n|[[Tanner Burns]]\n|[[Pitcher]]\n|[[Auburn Tigers baseball|Auburn]]\n|-\n|30\n|Carson Montgomery\n|[[Pitcher]]\n|[[Windermere High School]] ([[Florida|FL]])\n|}\n\n==First round selections==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:15%;\"\n|+Key\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#bfb;\"|*\n|Player did not sign\n|}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center; width=74%\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Pick\n! scope=\"col\"| Player\n! scope=\"col\"| Team\n! scope=\"col\"| Position\n! scope=\"col\"| School\n|-\n|1\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center\"|\n|[[Detroit Tigers]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|2\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center\"|\n|[[Baltimore Orioles]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|3\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center\"|\n|[[Miami Marlins]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|4\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center\"|\n|[[Kansas City Royals]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|5\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center\"|\n|[[Toronto Blue Jays]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|6\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center\"|\n|[[Seattle Mariners]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|7\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center\"|\n|[[Pittsburgh Pirates]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|8\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center\"|\n|[[San Diego Padres]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|9\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center\"|\n|[[Colorado Rockies]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|10\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center\"|\n|[[Los Angeles Angels]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|11\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center\"|\n|[[Chicago White Sox]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|12\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center